summary: This document is a daily log from the Metropolitan Correctional Center (MCC) in New York, dated August 9, 2019. It records inmate movements, status changes (including bail/bond, hospital transfers, and releases), and administrative actions. The log shows activity for numerous inmates identified by register numbers, but no real individual names are mentioned.

keyFacts: The document is a Bureau of Prisons (BOP) SENTRY system daily log from August 9, 2019.
It tracks inmate movements and status changes (e.g., bail/bond, hospital transfer, release) using register numbers, not names.
The log originates from facility NYMH3, which is the Metropolitan Correctional Center (MCC) in New York.
No real, named individuals are identified in this log; all references are to inmate register numbers (e.g., 105-940U, R01-001L).
The log shows routine prison administrative activity on a specific date.
